2.plot: After Pedro attacks Ceci, she is forced to leave East Los and stay in the women's shelter, abandoning the bomb squad.

3.title: End of an Era
3.plot: Maya is offered a job and Santa Fe and Jacob has to decide between her and home.

4.plot: Ceci comes back to East Los and proposes a coed Bomb Squad.

5.plot: After leaving the shelter, and having had enough of Fabiola, Ceci looks for a roommate elsewhere.

6.plot: The New coed bomb squad performs at the Valentines assembly to make their case for continued funding.

7.plot: Camila starts working off Nic's debt in order to keep him safe while he's in jail.

10.title: Mexifornia

11.title: Playing with My Balls
